# Spotify Webpage Clone

## Overview
This project is a Spotify-inspired webpage developed using only HTML5 and CSS3. It recreates the layout and design of the Spotify website to practice front-end web development and responsive web design.

## Features
- Responsive webpage layout
- Navigation bar
- Hero section
- Music cards and playlists
- Footer section
- Modern UI using HTML and CSS

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3

## Project Structure
```
spotify-clone/
│── index.html
│── spotify.css
│── images/
│── README.md
```

## How to Run
1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open `index.html` in any web browser.

